title: Avada v3.8.6.1 - Premium WordPress Themes
description:
Avada is the ultimate multi-purpose WordPress theme. It is clean, super flexible, responsive, includes Fusion Page Builder and comes packed with powerful options! This multi-purpose WordPress theme sets the new standard with endless possibilities. And its the most easy-to use theme on the market! Contains external links.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/themes/ directory
2. Activate the theme through the 'Themes' menu in WordPress
